long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Coreball, also known as Core Ball, is an online arcade game that helps you improve your targeting skills. The Coreball game was published by arealme.com in 2015.

There is a core ball that spins in the middle of the screen you just need to throw the small ball into the core ball without hitting any of the other balls that are attached to it.

Simply clicking anywhere on the screen will thrown the ball into the core ball.

The game has over 100 levels now. A level is completed once all the small balls are successfully attached to the core ball without any collisions.
